channel.title: Fake czar?
channel.description:
Just a quick thread, I was thinking. Since alot of newbs like czar...why not make a fake czar :o? Make it look exactly like czar but not really the source. More space in the client.java and maybe not even pimpscape source >.>...I found a perfect old server that I could use to make this fake czar. It sounds stupid and a waste of time but I'd like to think what people would say if I released a fake one. Calling me leecher and shit like that. Yet when they download it :| they'd be like, amg dis ain't czar.
What do you think :P?
